Name: mini_monyhar
Short Name: mini_monyhar
URL: https://monyhar.googlesource.com/monyhar/mini_monyhar/
Revision: See DEPS
License: BSD 3-clause
License File: mini_monyhar/LICENSE
Security Critical: yes

Description:
mini_monyhar is a small collection of useful low-level (“base”) routines from
the Chromium open-source project at https://www.monyhar.org/Home. Chromium is
large, sprawling, full of dependencies, and a web browser. mini_monyhar is
small, self-contained, and a library. mini_monyhar is especially useful as a
dependency of other code that wishes to use Chromium’s base routines.

Local Modifications:
None
